# This code is used to convert and analyze files from NIM_EASIRC.
#       2025.04.09 S.Nagao
#
#
# makeroot.cc : dat (or tar.xz) to rootfile converter
# UserAna.cc  : rootfile offline analyzer
#
### HOW TO ###
#
## Make execute files
# $ make
#    NOTE: libarchive-devel is necessary.
#
## Convert rootfile
# ./makeroot.sh input_name.dat (or .tar.xz)
#
## Analysis
# ./UserAna -f input_name.root
